Interface Functions.CheckedPredicate<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Argument type
    All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    Functions
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public static interface Functions.CheckedPredicate<T>
extends Serializable
    Checked version of java.util.function.Predicate. Essentially the same as CheckedFunction1<T, Boolean>, or short X1<T, Boolean>.
